* CloudWatch Logs

You can tag CloudWatch resources.

    You can now create tags in CloudWatch alarms that let you define policy
    controls for your AWS resources. This enables you to specify fine grained
    permissions, improving security for monitoring resources and cost allocation.
    Source: https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/whats-new/2019/04/you-can-now-use-resource-level-permissions-for-amazon-cloudwatch/

