* x-ray (tracing) and ServiceLens

- [[https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/aws/visualize-and-monitor-highly-distributed-applications-with-amazon-cloudwatch-servicelens/]]

AWS runs it's own version of tracing with x-ray and does a metric aggregation
via ServiceLens.

    CloudWatch ServiceLens ties together CloudWatch metrics and logs, as well as
    traces from AWS X-Ray.
    Source: Docs

X-ray have a trace maps, which enables you to visually map the end to end path
of a single request.
